                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-804-18530704 t18530704-804-punishment-45"></join>Confined One Year</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">DE LEENU</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18530704-804-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
